{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277097, "create_time": 1657078517, "is_blocked": true, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "", "timestamp": 1657078517}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277106, "create_time": 1657078793, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "固有长度：在与被测量物固连的惯性系中测得的长度\n运动长度：在其它惯性系中测得的长度", "timestamp": 1657078793}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277108, "create_time": 1657078838, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "测长度就是测量物体两端坐标的差值，要求位于两地的观察者同时测量，同时性的定义参考狭义相对论的对钟原则", "timestamp": 1657078838}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277129, "create_time": 1657079274, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "我理解书上的定义，但是实际使用就区分不了，比如图片中的问题，比如飞船发射信号时，以飞船为参考系的距离为运动长度，而信号被地球反射时，以飞船为参考系的距离为固有长度，这是为啥？", "timestamp": 1657079274}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277137, "create_time": 1657079572, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 这题你说固有长度就有点奇怪了，地球和飞船的距离是在变化的啊。如果实在搞不清楚，无脑上洛伦兹变换就是了。", "timestamp": 1657079572}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277212, "create_time": 1657080936, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 就是飞船发射信号时，以飞船为参考系距离为运动长度，以地球为参考系是固有长度，也就是前者乘gamma是后者，而信号被地球反射时，以飞船为参考系的距离为固有长度，以地球为参考系的为运动长度，前者除以gamma是后者。我用固有时转换到两个坐标分别算，脑子很清楚，结论就是他们的距离关系如我上面所说，但我感觉我不能直接从固有长度的角度来理解。", "timestamp": 1657080936}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277215, "create_time": 1657080982, "is_blocked": true, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "", "timestamp": 1657080982}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277350, "create_time": 1657083915, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 图片里面有描述，我文字中也描述了", "timestamp": 1657083915}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277355, "create_time": 1657084025, "is_blocked": true, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "", "timestamp": 1657084025}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277481, "create_time": 1657087059, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "从时间上来理解是不是会好一点，不同参考系的时间不同", "timestamp": 1657087059}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277574, "create_time": 1657089573, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 我指都是同一个事件下，以两个参考系来看的距离。比如飞船发射信号时，从地球、飞船分别来看的距离。不同事件不能比较。", "timestamp": 1657089573}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277578, "create_time": 1657089689, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯，我就是时间分两个坐标系做的，但做完回头看，发现同一事件下，它们的关系和固有长度与运动长度的关系一样。但有时候把地球参考系的当做固有长度，有时候把飞船参考系的当做固有长度。", "timestamp": 1657089689}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277605, "create_time": 1657090619, "is_blocked": true, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "", "timestamp": 1657090619}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277978, "create_time": 1657103156, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 哈哈哈我狭义相对论都忘得差不多了，实在搞不清楚的话就像Bob说的一样，无脑套洛伦兹变换就行了", "timestamp": 1657103156}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277979, "create_time": 1657103220, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 我记得舒幼生老师的《力学》对狭义相对论讲得是非常清楚的，推荐dz看看那的例题", "timestamp": 1657103220}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278225, "create_time": 1657112131, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 好的，谢谢啊", "timestamp": 1657112131}], "create_time": 1657078119, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657112131, "likenum": 8, "n_attentions": 8, "n_comments": 16, "pid": 78410, "poll": null, "reply": 16, "text": "相对论对距离是怎么定义的呢？究竟怎么区分固有长度和运动长度。\n![](https://bafkreiafgcsg2qcssi5m6kiojmwmgqsm2s7bkwyzz2uzauqkkrtti5i6m4.ipfs.infura-ipfs.io/?filename=dbce08ec8aeb172ded630b1c59eef8c75ebf9541pn%3D2%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26raww%3D960%26rawh%3D720%26aimh%3D720%26o%3Djpg_6%26type%3Dpic%26md5sum%3Dc64efdade72b66f4fc2a26ca44dc0f8e%26sign%3Db09be9e7cd%26png%3D62268-119164%26jpg%3D151435-294865.png&filetype=image%2Fpng) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafkreiafgcsg2qcssi5m6kiojmwmgqsm2s7bkwyzz2uzauqkkrtti5i6m4)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1657078119}}